short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Rev up your browser with the electrifying energy of a Girl Biker from Cyberpunk in this stunning Chrome extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Featuring a live wallpaper of a futuristic biker cruising through a neon-lit cityscape, this extension immerses you in the heart of the cyberpunk universe. Every new tab pulses with adrenaline and cyberpunk aesthetics.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpaper of a Cyberpunk Girl Biker in a vibrant, futuristic setting.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for a sleek and functional browsing experience.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts to your favorite websites.
Let the Girl Biker’s bold and daring style add a sense of adventure to your browsing sessions, with every new tab reflecting the thrill of the cyberpunk world. Perfect for fans of futuristic themes and neon cityscapes.
